{"tid":2070441,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日繼續掟麵包，不過輕力","createTime":"2020-06-19T06:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T06:40:37.000Z","uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3350e842f5ff31b1e516dc81ded7509772241280","tid":2070441,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:37:55.000Z","msg":"唔知將來會唔會大大力咁掟麵包呢？由7月1日起有更多人買麵包，一店獨大。阿姐會繼續幫公務員教訓肥信，將麵包掟爛後先俾我。"},{"pid":"cd8a10b71b8f030dbf0ce1692e003efc88cbbc35","tid":2070441,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:38:10.000Z","msg":"今朝見呢個阿姐負責拎麵包，一見到有人排隊就快快手咁招手過黎，相信她身有屎，希望透過快手拎麵包之速度掟麵包喎。<br />\n<br />\n呢個阿姐見掟一個麵包有50元收，當然拼命掟麵包，誰知今日掟出界勁尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n不過鴻圖道40號的麵包店執左，她以為我就會轉場?哦！寧願去便利店買麵包好過，好過一大朝早由公務員的替身俾「好心情」。"},{"pid":"81f9ecbd34319cabced66e3b799eaefbe2b051fd","tid":2070441,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:38:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【讓社工家棟看見我們的支持】眾籌登報聯署</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2070370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2070370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyziMpX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyziMpX.jpg&h=1fbdbdaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CuE3c4Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCuE3c4Y.jpg&h=d59182d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B6UiMpY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB6UiMpY.jpg&h=0c3a97ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOovCwx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOovCwx.png&h=3b1fe54d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b254e6bb521e5197acd09e128ccee3872314bf64","tid":2070441,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:38:35.000Z","msg":"今朝又見阿姐繼續掟麵包，而且相當大力。"},{"pid":"3b3034c367c9